~ PHI ~
http://js1k.com/demo/626

Creation and decay.
Watch these bold, organic patterns build up and etch away over time.

This visualisation uses the Golden Ratio, emerging from randomness, to determine the colour, position and intensity of its painted shapes and lines.

Click and hold the mouse for a burst of fresh colour. Refresh the page for a random tone. Let it run and run, for an ever-changing display.

In less than 1KB of JavaScript.

Golden Ratio: http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Golden_ratio
Source code: http://github.com/premasagar/js1k/
